Incomes of cooperatives and cooperative unions specified in point q clause 2 Article 12 of this Law in areas other than the areas specified in clause 3 Article 12 of this Law;
dd) Incomes of press agencies in the sectors and industries specified in point u clause 2 Article 12 of this Law;
